        "created_at": "2022-02-06T12:54:36.532Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m using flow to write my own codes, and if the ACTOR has no wait statement, it will prompt a warning message \u201cACTOR xxx does not contain a wait() statement\u201d, so I don\u2019t know if it\u2019s safe to just have ACTOR that does not contain a wait() statement</p>",
